data.title: Cecil Turner (1901-a1911)
data.meta_description: Birth of Cecil Turner in Edwinstowe, Nottinghamshire, UK in 1901
data.text:
Dates

Birth: January-March 1901 Edwinstowe, Nottinghamshire, UK

Father: Samuel Turner 1871-1928

Mother: Gertrude Antcliffe 1870-1953

Marriage: Unknown

Wife: Unknown

Death: After 1911

Children

None known

Notes

Birth of Cecil Turner in FreeBMD in January-March 1901 in Southwell (7b 460).

His sister was born in Edwinstowe in 1908.

In the 1911 census as Cecil Turner aged 10, born in Edwinstowe, Nottinghamshire, and living with his parents (Samuel and Gertrude), brother (Samuel), two sisters (Larna and Lucy Ellen), and widowed grandmother (May Robinson) in four rooms in Mill Lane, Edwinstowe Clipstone, Nottinghamshire.

There are four entries in Ancestry Public Member Trees for Cecil Turner.

Relationship

Cecil Turner was Felicity's fourth cousin twice removed.
